
mixin footer(spec)
	-
		spec = defaultTo(spec, {
			classes : '',
		});

	footer.footer(class=spec.classes)&attributes(attributes)
		h2.TK-visHid Site footer
		+ribbon()(class="-pattern -down")
			.grid.grid--space-between.grid--vAlign-center
				.footer__owner.grid__cell
					+owner
				.footer__share.grid__cell
					+share()

		+pageLayout()
			p.creds
				small
					| Original theme by #[a(href='https://twitter.com/jonrohan/') Jon Rohan] (although lots of alterations have been made to it)
